25:["$","h2","21",{"className":"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-10 mb-4 tracking-tight","children":"1. Tableau (G2 Rating: 4.4/5)"}]
26:["$","p","23",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Best for:"}]," Enterprise teams needing deep visual analytics and data storytelling."]}]
27:["$","p","25",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["Tableau remains the gold standard for data visualization. Its drag-and-drop interface lets you create complex dashboards without writing code, and its calculation language is powerful enough for advanced analysts."]}]
28:["$","p","27",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"What I like:"}]," The visualization capabilities are genuinely unmatched. Tableau's \"vizql\" engine can handle millions of rows of data smoothly. For data storytellers who need to communicate insights visually, there's nothing better. According to G2 reviews, Tableau scores 93% for data visualization quality — the highest in its category."]}]
29:["$","p","29",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"What I don't like:"}]," The pricing is aggressive. At $75/user/month for Creator licenses, a team of 20 costs $18,000/year before server costs. G2 users note that Tableau Server administration requires dedicated IT support. One reviewer from a healthcare organization said, \"Our Tableau environment needs a full-time admin. It's powerful but expensive to maintain.\""]}]
2a:["$","p","31",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Real user feedback:"}]," Capterra reviewers praise Tableau's ease of use for creating visualizations (4.5/5) but rate value for money lower at 3.8/5. Many note that Tableau Cloud (SaaS) has simplified deployment significantly versus the on-premise version."]}]
2b:["$","p","33",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Pricing:"}]," $75/user/month (Creator); $35/user/month (Explorer); $12/user/month (Viewer)."]}]
2c:["$","h2","35",{"className":"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-10 mb-4 tracking-tight","children":"2. Microsoft Power BI (G2 Rating: 4.5/5)"}]
2d:["$","p","37",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Best for:"}]," Organizations already invested in the Microsoft ecosystem."]}]
2e:["$","p","39",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["Power BI has rapidly closed the gap with Tableau, and in many ways surpassed it for Microsoft-centric organizations. Its DAX formula language is powerful for calculating custom metrics, and Power Query makes data transformation accessible to business users."]}]
2f:["$","p","41",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"What I like:"}]," The Office 365 integration is a killer feature. Power BI reports can be embedded directly in Teams, SharePoint, and PowerPoint. For organizations already on Microsoft 365, Power BI is often included or available at a fraction of Tableau's cost. G2 users rate Power BI 91% for ease of doing business with, the highest in the BI category."]}]
30:["$","p","43",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"What I don't like:"}]," Complex data models can be frustrating in Power BI. G2 reviews indicate that while Power BI is easy to start with, advanced DAX queries require significant expertise. Performance with very large datasets (10M+ rows) can lag behind Tableau."]}]
31:["$","p","45",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Pricing:"}]," $13.99/user/month (Pro); included with Microsoft 365 E5 ($57/user/month)."]}]
32:["$","h2","47",{"className":"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-10 mb-4 tracking-tight","children":"3. Looker (Google Cloud) (G2 Rating: 4.3/5)"}]
33:["$","p","49",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Best for:"}]," Companies needing embedded analytics and governed self-service at scale."]}]
34:["$","p","51",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["Looker (now part of Google Cloud) takes a unique approach: it defines all business logic in a modeling layer (LookML), ensuring everyone in the organization is working from the same definitions."]}]
35:["$","p","53",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"What I like:"}]," The LookML modeling layer is transformative for data governance. When \"revenue\" means the same thing in every dashboard, you eliminate the endless \"our numbers don't match\" conversations. For large organizations with complex data, this is a significant advantage. G2 users rate Looker 90% for data quality and governance features."]}]
36:["$","p","55",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"What I don't like:"}]," LookML has a steep learning curve for non-technical users. Unlike Tableau or Power BI, business users can't simply drag-and-drop to create visualizations — they need a modeler to define dimensions and measures first. Pricing is custom and typically starts at $3,000-5,000/month for small deployments."]}]
37:["$","p","57",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Pricing:"}]," Custom — expect $3,000+/month for standard deployments."]}]
38:["$","h2","59",{"className":"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-10 mb-4 tracking-tight","children":"4. Amplitude (G2 Rating: 4.6/5)"}]
39:["$","p","61",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Best for:"}]," Product teams wanting deep behavioral analytics."]}]
3a:["$","p","63",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["Amplitude is the leading product analytics platform, helping teams understand how users interact with their digital products. Its strength is behavioral cohort analysis, funnel analysis, and user pathing."]}]
3b:["$","p","65",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"What I like:"}]," Amplitude's ability to answer \"why\" questions about user behavior is unmatched. Its behavioral analytics let you segment users by actions, not just demographics. According to G2 reviews, Amplitude scores 94% for product analytics capabilities. One reviewer from a SaaS company said, \"Amplitude showed us exactly where users were dropping off in our onboarding flow — something our other analytics tools completely missed.\""]}]
3c:["$","p","67",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"What I don't like:"}]," Amplitude is expensive at scale. The free tier is generous (up to 10M events/month), but enterprise pricing can exceed $50,000/year. Setting up proper event tracking requires engineering effort and planning."]}]
3d:["$","p","69",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Pricing:"}]," Free (up to 10M events/month); Plus starts at $49/month; Growth at $1,079/month; Enterprise custom."]}]
3e:["$","h2","71",{"className":"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-10 mb-4 tracking-tight","children":"5. Mixpanel (G2 Rating: 4.5/5)"}]
3f:["$","p","73",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Best for:"}]," Mid-market product teams needing powerful analytics without enterprise pricing."]}]
40:["$","p","75",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["Mixpanel offers similar behavioral analytics to Amplitude but with a more accessible pricing model. Its data modeling and reporting interface has been significantly modernized."]}]
41:["$","p","77",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"What I like:"}]," Mixpanel's pricing is more accessible for mid-market teams. The free tier supports up to 100K tracked users (not events), which is more generous than it sounds for early-stage products. G2 users rate Mixpanel 4.5/5, praising its report builder for being \"easy to use without sacrificing depth.\""]}]
42:["$","p","79",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"What I don't like:"}]," Like Amplitude, Mixpanel requires upfront event instrumentation. G2 reviews note that data migration and schema changes can be painful. Customer support response times are a common complaint in lower-tier plans."]}]
43:["$","p","81",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Pricing:"}]," Free (up to 100K MTUs); Growth starts at $28/month; Enterprise custom."]}]
44:["$","h2","83",{"className":"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-10 mb-4 tracking-tight","children":"6. Metabase (G2 Rating: 4.5/5)"}]
45:["$","p","85",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Best for:"}]," Teams wanting a free, open-source analytics layer."]}]
46:["$","p","87",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["Metabase is the most popular open-source business intelligence tool. It connects directly to your database and lets anyone on the team ask questions through a simple interface — no SQL required."]}]
47:["$","p","89",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"What I like:"}]," Metabase is remarkably easy to set up (deploy in 5 minutes) and costs nothing for self-hosted use. According to Capterra, users rate Metabase 4.5/5 and praise its simplicity: \"We went from zero analytics capability to company-wide dashboards in an afternoon.\" For startups and small teams, it's the perfect entry point."]}]
48:["$","p","91",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"What I don't like:"}]," Lacks the depth of enterprise BI tools. Advanced visualizations, complex data modeling, and row-level security are limited. For organizations with complex data needs, Metabase works best as a self-service layer alongside a more powerful tool."]}]
49:["$","p","93",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Pricing:"}]," Free (open-source, self-hosted); Cloud plans start at $85/month (Starter), $500/month (Business)."]}]
4a:["$","h2","95",{"className":"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-10 mb-4 tracking-tight","children":"7. Domo (G2 Rating: 4.2/5)"}]
4b:["$","p","97",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Best for:"}]," All-in-one BI combining data integration, visualization, and collaboration."]}]
4c:["$","p","99",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["Domo positions itself as a complete BI platform that goes beyond visualization to include data integration (ETL), app building, and collaboration features."]}]
4d:["$","p","101",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"What I like:"}]," Domo's all-in-one approach is attractive for teams that want a single platform for all their analytics needs. Its mobile app is excellent — one of the best in the BI category. G2 reviews note that Domo's time-to-insight is faster than Tableau for common analytics use cases."]}]
4e:["$","p","103",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"What I don't like:"}]," Domo's custom pricing model makes cost comparison difficult. G2 reviews rate value for money at 76% (below Tableau and Power BI). Users also note that migrating data into Domo's platform can be a lock-in risk."]}]
4f:["$","p","105",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Pricing:"}]," Custom — expect $300-500/user/year for standard deployments."]}]
50:["$","h2","107",{"className":"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-10 mb-4 tracking-tight","children":"8. Sisense (G2 Rating: 4.3/5)"}]
51:["$","p","109",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Best for:"}]," Independent software vendors (ISVs) needing embedded analytics."]}]
52:["$","p","111",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["Sisense specializes in embedded analytics — allowing SaaS companies to add dashboards and reports directly into their own products. Its single-stack architecture handles large datasets efficiently."]}]
53:["$","p","113",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"What I like:"}]," If you're building a SaaS product and want to offer analytics features to your customers, Sisense is purpose-built for this. G2 reviews rate Sisense 87% for embedded analytics capabilities. The platform's ability to handle billions of rows on commodity hardware is impressive."]}]
54:["$","p","115",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"What I don't like:"}]," Not ideal for internal BI use cases — it's overkill if you just need standard dashboards for your team. Pricing is opaque, and setup requires technical expertise."]}]
55:["$","p","117",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Pricing:"}]," Custom."]}]
56:["$","h2","119",{"className":"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-10 mb-4 tracking-tight","children":"9. Qlik Sense (G2 Rating: 4.3/5)"}]
57:["$","p","121",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Best for:"}]," Organizations needing associative data exploration."]}]
58:["$","p","123",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["Qlik Sense uses a unique associative engine that doesn't require pre-defined queries. You can explore data freely, and Qlik automatically surfaces connections and relationships between data points."]}]
59:["$","p","125",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"What I like:"}]," Qlik's associative model is genuinely different and powerful for exploratory analysis. When you select a data point, Qlik highlights both related and unrelated data, often revealing unexpected insights. G2 users rate Qlik 88% for data exploration."]}]
5a:["$","p","127",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"What I don't like:"}]," The user interface feels dated compared to Tableau and Power BI. Qlik's scripting language for data transformation has a steeper learning curve than Power Query or Tableau Prep."]}]
5b:["$","p","129",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Pricing:"}]," $30/user/month (Business); Enterprise custom."]}]
5c:["$","h2","131",{"className":"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-10 mb-4 tracking-tight","children":"10. Heap (G2 Rating: 4.3/5)"}]
5d:["$","p","133",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Best for:"}]," Teams wanting auto-captured analytics without manual event tracking."]}]
5e:["$","p","135",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["Heap automatically captures every user interaction (clicks, taps, page views, form submissions) — no need to instrument events upfront. You define events retroactively with a visual interface."]}]
5f:["$","p","137",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"What I like:"}]," The auto-capture feature is a game-changer for teams that struggle with event instrumentation. You never have to go back to engineering to add tracking for a new analysis. G2 users rate Heap 89% for data capture, and one reviewer noted: \"Heap saved our product team two months of engineering work just in the first quarter.\""]}]
60:["$","p","139",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"What I don't like:"}]," Auto-capture generates massive data volumes, which drives up costs at scale. Advanced analysis features are less powerful than Amplitude or Mixpanel. Data governance can be challenging with everything captured."]}]
61:["$","p","141",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Pricing:"}]," Free tier available; Growth starts at custom pricing; Enterprise custom."]}]
62:["$","h2","143",{"className":"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-10 mb-4 tracking-tight","children":"How I Evaluated These Platforms"}]
63:["$","p","145",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["I selected these 10 tools based on G2 Grid Reports, Gartner Magic Quadrant for Analytics & BI, and hands-on testing. My evaluation considered:"]}]
64:["$","p","147",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["- ",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Analytics depth"}]," (30%) — Can it answer complex business questions?"]}]
65:["$","p","148",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["- ",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Ease of use"}]," (25%) — How quickly can non-technical team members get value?"]}]
66:["$","p","149",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["- ",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Data integration"}]," (20%) — How easily does it connect to your data sources?"]}]
67:["$","p","150",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["- ",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Value for money"}]," (15%) — Does pricing match the value delivered?"]}]
68:["$","p","151",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["- ",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Scalability"}]," (10%) — Can it handle growing data volumes?"]}]
69:["$","h2","153",{"className":"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-10 mb-4 tracking-tight","children":"How to Choose"}]
6a:["$","p","155",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Choose Tableau if:"}]," Data visualization quality is your top priority and you have budget for enterprise licensing and admin support."]}]
6b:["$","p","157",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Choose Power BI if:"}]," Your organization runs on Microsoft 365 and you need a cost-effective BI solution that integrates seamlessly."]}]
6c:["$","p","159",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Choose Amplitude if:"}]," You're a product-led company that needs deep behavioral analytics to understand user journeys."]}]
6d:["$","p","161",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Choose Metabase if:"}]," You're a startup or small team that needs basic self-serve analytics without spending a dime."]}]
6e:["$","p","163",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Choose Looker if:"}]," You need governed, consistent analytics at enterprise scale with a single source of truth for business definitions."]}]
6f:["$","h2","165",{"className":"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-10 mb-4 tracking-tight","children":"FAQ"}]
70:["$","p","167",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Q: What's the difference between BI tools and product analytics tools?"}],""]}]
71:["$","p","168",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["A: BI tools (Tableau, Power BI, Looker) are designed for structured reporting on business data (sales, finance, operations). Product analytics tools (Amplitude, Mixpanel, Heap) focus on user behavior — how people interact with your product. Most organizations need both."]}]
72:["$","p","170",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Q: Can I use Tableau and Power BI together?"}],""]}]
73:["$","p","171",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["A: Yes, though most teams standardize on one. Some large enterprises use Power BI for standard reporting and Tableau for complex data visualization needs."]}]
74:["$","p","173",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Q: What's the best free analytics tool?"}],""]}]
75:["$","p","174",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["A: Metabase (self-hosted) and the free tiers of Power BI, Amplitude, and Mixpanel are all excellent entry points."]}]
76:["$","p","176",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["*Sources: G2 Business Intelligence Grid Report (Spring 2026), Capterra Analytics Reviews (2026), Gartner Magic Quadrant for ABI Platforms (2026). All ratings reflect user experiences as of May 2026.*"]}]
